###############################################################################
# Round 6 — 결제(PG 연동) API
#
# ▶ 실행 절차 (주말 복기용)
#   1) 인프라 기동:   docker compose -f docker/infra-compose.yml up -d
#   2) PG 전용 DB:    docker exec -i docker-mysql-1 mysql -uroot -proot -e \
#                       "CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS paymentgateway; \
#                        GRANT ALL ON paymentgateway.* TO 'application'@'%'; FLUSH PRIVILEGES;"
#   3) Gradle JVM:    JDK 21 사용 (IntelliJ: Settings > Build Tools > Gradle > Gradle JVM = temurin-21)
#                     CLI: JAVA_HOME=.../temurin-21.0.11/Contents/Home
#   4) PG 기동:       ./gradlew :apps:pg-simulator:bootRun    (8082)
#   5) commerce 기동: ./gradlew :apps:commerce-api:bootRun    (8080)
#
# ▶ 결제는 PENDING 주문이 있어야 함. 테스트용 주문 생성(SQL):
#   docker exec -i docker-mysql-1 mysql -uroot -proot loopers -e \
#     "INSERT INTO orders (created_at,updated_at,discount_amount,final_amount,total_amount,user_id,status)
#      VALUES (now(6),now(6),0,5000,5000,1,'PENDING'); SELECT LAST_INSERT_ID();"
###############################################################################

@commerceApi = http://localhost:8080
@pgSimulator = http://localhost:8082

### 1. 결제 요청 (orderId 는 위에서 만든 PENDING 주문 id 로 교체)
#   - 접수 성공: status=PROCESSING + transactionKey
#   - PG 장애/CB OPEN: status=PENDING (HTTP 는 항상 200 — Fallback)
POST {{commerceApi}}/api/v1/payments
X-Loopers-UserId: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9814-1451"
}

### 2. 상태 수동 복구 (콜백 유실/타임아웃 건을 PG에 재조회해 동기화)
POST {{commerceApi}}/api/v1/payments/recover

### 3. (참고) PG 콜백 — 보통 PG가 자동 호출. 수동 재현용.
POST {{commerceApi}}/api/v1/payments/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionKey": "20260626:TR:xxxxxx",
  "orderId": "000001",
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9814-1451",
  "amount": 5000,
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "reason": "정상 승인되었습니다."
}

###############################################################################
# PG-Simulator 직접 호출 (디버깅용)
###############################################################################

### 4. PG 결제 요청 직접 (약 60% 성공 / 40% 500)
POST {{pgSimulator}}/api/v1/payments
X-USER-ID: loopers-commerce
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "000001",
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9814-1451",
  "amount": 5000,
  "callbackUrl": "http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/callback"
}

### 5. PG 결제 단건 조회 (txKey 교체)
GET {{pgSimulator}}/api/v1/payments/20260626:TR:xxxxxx
X-USER-ID: loopers-commerce

### 6. PG 주문별 결제 조회
GET {{pgSimulator}}/api/v1/payments?orderId=000001
X-USER-ID: loopers-commerce
